    "name": "The Grappler",
    "steam_appid": 3298230,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298230/extras/2ce6f87478b04ef02c69962f00eac33f.poster.avif?t=1748316651\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298230/extras/2ce6f87478b04ef02c69962f00eac33f.webm?t=1748316651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298230/extras/2ce6f87478b04ef02c69962f00eac33f.mp4?t=1748316651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demo does not contain all game features. First trailer showcases full game features, second showcases demo</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grapple</strong> or<strong> Fall</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Grappler</strong> is  a test of patience, precision, and perseverance. Inspired by brutally challenging platformers like <i>Jump King</i> and <i>Getting Over It</i>, with movement mechanics inspired by <i>Celeste</i>, this 2D adventure will push you to your limits, one frustratingly rewarding grapple at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the top of the mountain using only your grappling hook, double jump, and dash. Sounds simple, right? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grappling Hook</strong>: Use your grappling hook to swing yourself across gaps and terrain.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Double Jump &amp; Dash</strong>: Combine your jumps and dashes to create fluid, skill-based movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Difficult</strong>: The higher you climb, the more intense the challenge becomes. A single mistake could send you plummeting back to the bottom—so stay focused!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful but Unforgiving Areas</strong>: Traverse different biomes, from forests to icy peaks, each with its own unique hazards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer Ghosts</strong>: Race your friends asynchronously up the mountain by importing their ghosts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secret Area</strong>: For the truly skilled, who reach the summit at blazing speed.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you conquer the mountain, or will gravity get the best of you? The summit is waiting—if you can survive the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298230/extras/e09dbba17a981eaef1b553a93be0c124.poster.avif?t=1748316651\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298230/extras/e09dbba17a981eaef1b553a93be0c124.webm?t=1748316651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298230/extras/e09dbba17a981eaef1b553a93be0c124.mp4?t=1748316651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
